headline: Camden Property Trust to Participate in Nareit REITweek Conference
summary: HOUSTON, May 30, 2025--Camden Property Trust (NYSE:CPT) (the "Company") announced today it will participate in the Nareit REITweek 2025 Investor Conference on Tuesday, June 3 and Wednesday, June 4, 2025. The Company posted an updated Investor Presentation in conjunction with this event, which includes operating and transactions updates, and is available in the Investors section of the Company’s website.
